  "fullSource": "use IO.Std.write_line;\n\nfetch_async(x: int) -> Tasks.TASK[int] => x * x;\n\nsum_of_squares(xs: Collections.List[int]) -> Tasks.TASK[int] is\n    let total mut = 0;\n\n    for x in xs do\n        let await y = fetch_async(x);\n        total = total + y;\n    od\n\n    return total;\nsi\n\nentry() is\n    let result = sum_of_squares([1, 2, 3, 4]).result;\n\n    write_line(\"sum_of_squares = {result}\");\nsi\n",
